title: WR Rankings: 11-20 + Draft Sweet Spots, #BeastHood - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/8
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason discuss and debate wide receiver rankings! Find out which mid-round WRs have the best chance at being value picks in fantasy football drafts! Courtland Sutton or Jerry Jeudy? Will D.J. Moore find the endzone more with Baker Mayfield at QB? Plus, the latest news out of training camp as Preseason Week 1 is right around the corner! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 8th, 2022

The 2022 Ultimate Draft Kit and Draft Analyzer are available NOW
